---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About Us - PickMyAITools"
  description="Learn about PickMyAITools, our mission to help you find the perfect AI tools, and our commitment to unbiased reviews."
  canonical="/about"
>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-4xl">
    <article class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">About PickMyAITools</h1>
      
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-6">
        PickMyAITools is dedicated to helping individuals and businesses find the perfect AI tools for their specific needs.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        With hundreds of AI tools available, choosing the right one can be overwhelming. We provide expert reviews, detailed comparisons, and personalized recommendations to simplify your decision-making process.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">What We Do</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-6">
        <li>Comprehensive reviews of AI tools across multiple categories</li>
        <li>Side-by-side comparisons to help you choose between options</li>
        <li>Use-case specific recommendations</li>
        <li>Guides and resources to help you get started with AI</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Our Approach</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        We test and evaluate AI tools based on real-world use cases, considering factors like ease of use, features, pricing, and value. Our goal is to provide honest, unbiased information to help you make informed decisions.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        Have questions or suggestions? We'd love to hear from you. Please reach out through our contact form or social media channels.
      </p>
    </article>
  </div>
</Layout>
